BILLING_EVENTS.description: Contains billing event records for user transactions and charges

columns.business_description: Unique identifier for each billing event
Foreign key reference to the user who triggered the billing event
Type of billing event (e.g., subscription, usage, refund)
Monetary amount associated with the billing event
Date when the billing event occurred
Timestamp when the record was first loaded into the system
Timestamp when the record was last updated
Source system from which the billing event data originated

FEATURE_USAGE.description: Tracks usage of various features within meetings

columns.business_description: Unique identifier for each feature usage record
Foreign key reference to the meeting where feature was used
Name of the feature that was used
Number of times the feature was used in the meeting
Date when the feature usage occurred
Timestamp when the record was first loaded into the system
Timestamp when the record was last updated
Source system from which the feature usage data originated

LICENSES.description: Manages software licenses assigned to users

columns.business_description: Unique identifier for each license
Type or tier of the license
Foreign key reference to the user assigned this license
Date when the license becomes active
Date when the license expires
Timestamp when the record was first loaded into the system
Timestamp when the record was last updated
Source system from which the license data originated

MEETINGS.description: Contains information about meetings and video conferences

columns.business_description: Unique identifier for each meeting
Foreign key reference to the user who hosted the meeting
Subject or topic of the meeting
Timestamp when the meeting started
Timestamp when the meeting ended
Duration of the meeting in minutes
Timestamp when the record was first loaded into the system
Timestamp when the record was last updated
Source system from which the meeting data originated

PARTICIPANTS.description: Tracks participants in meetings and their attendance details

columns.business_description: Unique identifier for each participant record
Foreign key reference to the meeting
Foreign key reference to the user who participated
Timestamp when the participant joined the meeting
Timestamp when the participant left the meeting
Timestamp when the record was first loaded into the system
Timestamp when the record was last updated
Source system from which the participant data originated

SUPPORT_TICKETS.description: Manages customer support tickets and their resolution status

columns.business_description: Unique identifier for each support ticket
Foreign key reference to the user who created the ticket
Category or type of the support ticket
Current status of the ticket resolution
Date when the support ticket was opened
Timestamp when the record was first loaded into the system
Timestamp when the record was last updated
Source system from which the support ticket data originated

USERS.description: Contains user account information and profile details

columns.business_description: Unique identifier for each user account
Display name of the user
Email address of the user
Company or organization the user belongs to
Subscription plan type of the user
Timestamp when the record was first loaded into the system
Timestamp when the record was last updated
Source system from which the user data originated

markdown_format.BILLING_EVENTS:
# BILLING_EVENTS
| Column Name | Business Description | Data Type | Constraints | Domain Values |
|-------------|---------------------|-----------|-------------|---------------|
| EVENT_ID | Unique identifier for each billing event | VARCHAR(16777216) | Primary Key, Not Null | N/A |
| USER_ID | Foreign key reference to the user who triggered the billing event | VARCHAR(16777216) | Foreign Key, Not Null | N/A |
| EVENT_TYPE | Type of billing event (e.g., subscription, usage, refund) | VARCHAR(16777216) | Not Null | subscription, usage, refund, credit |
| AMOUNT | Monetary amount associated with the billing event | VARCHAR(16777216) | Not Null | N/A |
| EVENT_DATE | Date when the billing event occurred | DATE | Not Null | N/A |
| LOAD_TIMESTAMP | Timestamp when the record was first loaded into the system | TIMESTAMP_NTZ(9) | Not Null | N/A |
| UPDATE_TIMESTAMP | Timestamp when the record was last updated | TIMESTAMP_NTZ(9) | Nullable | N/A |
| SOURCE_SYSTEM | Source system from which the billing event data originated | VARCHAR(16777216) | Not Null | billing_system, payment_gateway, subscription_service |
markdown_format.FEATURE_USAGE:

| USAGE_DATE | Date when the feature usage occurred | DATE | Not Null | N/A |

| UPDATE_TIMESTAMP | Timestamp when the record was last updated | TIMESTAMP_NTZ(9) | Nullable | N/A |
| SOURCE_SYSTEM | Source system from which the feature usage data originated | VARCHAR(16777216) | Not Null | meeting_platform, analytics_service |
